<h2>The "Basic Kolion"</h2>

<p>
Briefly:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Kolion token issued on Waves blockchain;
<li>1 million - the total number of tokens Kolion;
<li>of which 500'000 - investors; 500'000 - remains in reserve;
<li>for every euro invested in the ICO, the investor receives 1 Kolion;
<li>contributions can be made in the Waves' tokens in Bitcoins, in rubles and euros.
</ul>

<p>
The purpose of the project: the purchase of land and buildings of the recreation and health in Kolionovo, bringing them into the proper form (repair), the completion of the baths, etc. For successful implementation of the project required an investment of 500'000 EUR.
</p>

<p>
Approximate cost estimates, eur:
</p>

<ul>
<li>160'000 – redemption of the remaining property and land of 4 hectares;
<li>30'000 – the creation of new or restoration of utilities (electricity, water, heating, sewage, internet);
<li>110'000 – reconstruction and equipment of the hotel with half-board with 20 seats in the winter and 50 in summer. Total of 250 square meters;
<li>160'000 – production modules (fish ponds, plant for processing, refrigerators, warehouses, hangars facilities for animals, greenhouses, etc.);
<li>16'000 – landscaping with the creation of the commercial "spots" (fishing, workshops, tree houses, sauna, etc .;
<li>15'000 – construction of houses for rent;
<li>60'000 – repair, reconstruction and equipping of auxiliary building of 300 square meters;
<li>30'000 – repair and rehabilitation of an industrial building of 100 square meters;
<li>14'000 – breeding herd, trees, rocks, seeds, equipment, materials, consumables, fuel, etc.
</ul>

<p>
Full provision of the entire amount of investment goods and the available machines.
</p>


<h3>Additional conditions:</h3>

<ol>
<li>Tokens (coupons) are not in cash or shares.
<li>Tokens can be exchanged for products (goods and services) in farms Kolionovo and a recreation center and health Kolionovo on the attached price list.
<li>A set of products (goods and services) will eventually be supplemented.
<li>Holders tokens Kolion monthly receive a variety of gifts and savings "bonuses" from the farm and the base Kolionovo. For example in 1000 the holders Kolion: 2 eggs as a gift, plus a 0.1 ticket to the Tractor biathlon, plus 0.02 goose, etc. Shares and gifts are not specified in advance. Information will be posted later. Follow the news.
<li>Kolion Tokens can be freely exchanged for certain commodity Koliony. Such as GuseKoleon, YaytsaKolion, BanyaKolino, DubKolion, BiatlonKolion etc. Product kolion can be obtained upon presentation of a pre-agreed time. Quantity of each commodity kolionov limited.
</ol>

